               <p>Before Lord Chief Justice Tenderden.</p>
               <p>1960. 
               
                  <persName id="t18311020-4-defend145" type="defendantName">
                     JOHN 
                     KYBERT
                  <interp inst="t18311020-4-defend145" type="surname" value="KYBERT"></interp>
